      "file_path": "kubernetes/dcaegen2-services/common/dcaegen2-services-common/templates/_deployment.tpl",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 323,
      "message": "This solution will cause application to load app-config from app-config-input (ConfigMap) and not from app-config (emptyDir). Nonetheless envSubst will transform app-config-input (ConfigMap ) in to app-config (emptyDir) that is used in init-consul. We can remove envSubst container and mount app-config-input (ConfigMap) directly in to init-consul, if that is not a problem.",
